data.description: Welcome home to this inviting 3-bedroom, 2-bath gem built in 2012. This beautifully maintained residence boasts a wealth of features that make it stand out from the rest, to include; durable granite countertops in the kitchen, tile flooring throughout the entire home for easy maintenance, no carpet!  A private, fenced backyard, this home is conveniently close to  schools, parks, shopping, and all the amenities you desire.  Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this your forever home!
